name: 🐙 Octopus Ramen 🐙
description:
Ah.... Why I am here?
Well, I was lost in an alley full of old shops nearby Osaka.

I accidentally saw a weird old ramen shop. So I was just glancing at a menu. It was ramen with the black soup which I've never tried before. Because of hunger and my weird thought, I then got in and try such black ramen even though I cannot read any Japanese.

Surprisingly, it was such a weird ramen shop!! with an octopus chef !? His 8 tentacles were moving so fast. All the Fish Head customers were insanely eating and slurping the black ramen, unlike a human (Well, they're not a human though).

But wait, is the black soup was made of ink from the chef himself???

Should I try it?
